  <summary date="2004-02-23T17:26:03Z" status="Introduced in House">Directs the Secretary of Transportation to establish a flexibility incentive grant pilot program to encourage States to establish new sources of revenue for transit projects and services. Directs the Secretary to make grants to States that: (1) increase their expenditures for transit projects and other services; or (2) dedicate State revenues specifically for transit projects and services.</summary>
